
BEFORE RUNNING ANY VERIFICATION/VALIDATION, PLEASE EDIT <sideband_dir>/source/rtl/iosfsbc/common/sbc_map.sv
=============================================================================================================
FILE TO REPLACE SBC_*_CELL WITH TARGET PROCESS SPECIFIC CTECH CELLS.
